article_title: Rochester lags behind as state adds jobs
article_text:
However, while Rochester faulted over the past year, statewide, job numbers improved with nearly 20,000 jobs added in February alone. State officials say job totals reached an all-time record.

Rochester showed the biggest drop over the course of the year while most of the new jobs being added in New York City.
